{
  "texts": [
    "Human-human interaction.",
    "For level 1, the responses in the first level of the human-human interaction were the same as those in the human-AI interaction.",
    "For level 2, participants first performed the same procedure as in level 1.",
    "Next, they were presented with 100 arrays of 12 faces for 500 ms, followed by the response of another participant from level 1 to the same array, which was presented for 2 s (Fig. 1b).",
    "On each trial, the total numbers of more sad and more happy classifications of the other participants (up until that trial) were presented at the bottom of the screen."
  ]
}